The association between Hp (Table 1
) and SAA (Table 2
) and weight gain for the overall (Model 1), prepatent (Model 2), and patent period (Model 3) was investigated by calculating the AUC. Weight gains of the three infection groups can be found in the electronic supplements (Fig. 2S). A negative association between Hp and weight gain was observed during the overall and patent periods, but not during the prepatent period. Similarly, the model for SAA revealed a negative association with weight gain during the patent period. There were no significant interactions between infection groups and APPs in the models.
